rules.natural: Either the farm cooperative produces corn or the corn is edible.

Whenever it is not the case that food safety regulation implies that not being raw product or ready to eat implies pre-cooked leads to processed product, then the corn has compliance exception.

If it is not the case that not having export restricted implies not domestic only leads to not having banned export, then the corn does not have special permit.
